@sainak In this particular case, although commenting out is_property field of Bed Model will not affect the results of **ConsultationBedSerializer**, as we are going to handle the is_occupied property of Bed in this serializer.

But in other serializers like **AssetBedSerializer, PatientAssetBedSerializer**, which are also using **BedSerializer**, since we are not handling the is_occupied property of Bed in these serializers, so it will always correspond to the False (the default value).

What are your thoughts?
